nodes.text: Sheel was a female Tarasin and a member of the Wyrd. She lead a group of Wyrd members who were transported aboard a Separatist CR90 corvette, to discuss an alliance between the Wyrd and the Separatists. After the corvette was attacked while in the Ando system, Sheel and the Wyrd she lead were some of the few survivors and they attacked the Heroes of Cularin when they boarded the ship.
